{"word":"Mountains and Hills","slug":"mountains-and-hills","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Mountains and Hills</b> - <b>(A) NAMES OF</b><p/><b>ABARIM,</b> east of Jordan<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=27&verse=12'>Num 27:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=33&verse=48'>Num 33:48</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=49'>Deu 32:49</a><p/><b>ARARAT,</b> in Armenia<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=8&verse=4'>Gen 8:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=51&verse=27'>Jer 51:27</a><p/><b>BASHAN</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=68&verse=15'>Ps 68:15</a><p/><b>BETHEL</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=13&verse=2'>1Sa 13:2</a><p/><b>CARMEL,</b> on the seacoast of Palestine<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=18&verse=19'>1Ki 18:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=2&verse=25'>2Ki 2:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=19&verse=23'>2Ki 19:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=33&verse=9'>Isa 33:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=46&verse=18'>Jer 46:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=50&verse=19'>Jer 50:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=1&verse=2'>Amo 1:2</a><p/><b>EBAL,</b> in Samaria<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=11&verse=29'>Deu 11:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=27&verse=4'>Deu 27:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=8&verse=30'>Jos 8:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=8&verse=33'>Jos 8:33</a><p/><b>EPHRAIM,</b> in central Palestine<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=17&verse=15'>Jos 17:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=2&verse=9'>Jdg 2:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=4&verse=5'>Jdg 4:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=7&verse=24'>Jdg 7:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=18&verse=13'>Jdg 18:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=12&verse=25'>1Ki 12:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=5&verse=22'>2Ki 5:22</a><p/><b>GERIZIM,</b> in Samaria<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=11&verse=29'>Deu 11:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=27&verse=12'>Deu 27:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=8&verse=33'>Jos 8:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=9&verse=7'>Jdg 9:7</a><p/><b>GILBOA,</b> on which Saul died<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=28&verse=4'>1Sa 28:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=31&verse=1'>1Sa 31:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=1&verse=6'>2Sa 1:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=1&verse=21'>2Sa 1:21</a><p/><b>GILEAD</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=31&verse=21'>Gen 31:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=31&verse=25'>Gen 31:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=7&verse=3'>Jdg 7:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=22&chapter=4&verse=1'>Son 4:1</a><p/><b>HERMON</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=3&verse=8'>Deu 3:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=11&verse=17'>Jos 11:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=13&verse=11'>Jos 13:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=133&verse=3'>Psa 133:3</a><p/><b>HOR,</b> Aaron's burial place<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=20&verse=22'>Num 20:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=21&verse=4'>Num 21:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=33&verse=37'>Num 33:37</a><p/><b>HOREB,</b> Sinai or Mount of God<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=3&verse=1'>Exo 3:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=17&verse=6'>Exo 17:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=4&verse=10'>Deu 4:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=5&verse=2'>Deu 5:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=9&verse=8'>Deu 9:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=8&verse=9'>1Ki 8:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=8'>1Ki 19:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=5&verse=10'>2Ch 5:10</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=106&verse=19'>Psa 106:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=4&verse=4'>Mal 4:4</a><p/><b>LEBANON</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=3&verse=25'>Deu 3:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=3&verse=3'>Jdg 3:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=5&verse=14'>1Ki 5:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=17&verse=3'>Eze 17:3</a><p/><b>MIZAR</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=42&verse=6'>Ps 42:6</a><p/><b>MORIAH,</b> in Jerusalem, where the temple was built and where it is<p/>supposed Abraham offered up Isaac<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=22&verse=2'>Gen 22:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=24&verse=18'>2Sa 24:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=21&verse=18'>1Ch 21:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=22&verse=1'>1Ch 22:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=3&verse=1'>2Ch 3:1</a><p/><b>NEBO</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=49'>Deu 32:49</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=34&verse=1'>Deu 34:1</a><p/><b>OLIVES, OR OLIVET</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=21&verse=1'>Mat 21:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=24&verse=3'>Mat 24:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=30'>Mat 26:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=21&verse=37'>Luk 21:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=12'>Act 1:12</a><p/><b>PISGAH,</b> in Moab, from whence Moses viewed the Promised Land<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=21&verse=20'>Num 21:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=23&verse=14'>Num 23:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=3&verse=27'>Deu 3:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=4&verse=49'>Deu 4:49</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=34&verse=1'>Deu 34:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=12&verse=3'>Jos 12:3</a><p/><b>SEIR</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=14&verse=6'>Gen 14:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=1&verse=2'>Deu 1:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=2&verse=5'>Deu 2:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=35&verse=2'>Eze 35:2</a><p/><b>SINAI,</b> upon which Moses received the Decalogue<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=16&verse=1'>Exo 16:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=19&verse=11'>Exo 19:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=24&verse=16'>Exo 24:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=31&verse=18'>Exo 31:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=7&verse=38'>Lev 7:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=26&verse=46'>Lev 26:46</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=9&verse=13'>Neh 9:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=38'>Act 7:38</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Horeb, <p/><b>TABOR</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=4&verse=6'>Jdg 4:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=4&verse=14'>Jdg 4:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=8&verse=18'>Jdg 8:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=89&verse=12'>Psa 89:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=46&verse=18'>Jer 46:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=5&verse=1'>Hos 5:1</a><p/><b>ZION,</b> or Sion<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=5&verse=7'>2Sa 5:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=8&verse=1'>1Ki 8:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=87&verse=2'>Psa 87:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=11&verse=26'>Rom 11:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=12&verse=22'>Heb 12:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=14&verse=1'>Rev 14:1</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Jerusalem, JERUSALEM<p/><b>(B) SCENES OF GREAT EVENTS</b><p/><b>ON Ararat,</b> the ark rested<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=8&verse=4'>Ge 8:4</a><p/>-- <b>Moriah,</b> Abraham sacrificed Isaac<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=22&verse=2'>Ge 22:2</a><p/>-- <b>Horeb,</b> Moses saw the Burning Bush<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=3&verse=1'>Exo 3:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=3&verse=2'>Exo 3:2</a><p/>-- <b>Sinai,</b> the Law was given<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=19&verse=11'>Exo 19:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=19&verse=20'>Exo 19:20</a><p/>-- <b>Ebal and Gerizim,</b> were read the Blessings and Curses<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=11&verse=29'>Deu 11:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=27&verse=11'>Deu 27:11-13</a><p/>-- <b>Carmel,</b> occurred Elijah's sacrifice<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=18&verse=19'>1Ki 18:19</a><p/>-- <b>Hermon</b> or Tabor, Christ was Transfigured<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=9&verse=2'>Mr 9:2</a><p/>-- <b>Olivet,</b> occurred Christ's ascension<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=12'>Ac 1:12</a>"}]}